trans-unit.source: Encapsulates all Access Control Entry (ACE) types currently defined by Microsoft Corporation.
trans-unit.target: 封裝 Microsoft Corporation 目前定義的所有存取控制項目 (ACE) 型別。

trans-unit.source: All <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> objects contain a 32-bit access mask and a <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 所有的 <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> 物件都包含 32 位元的存取遮罩和 <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the access mask for this <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定這個 <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> 物件的存取遮罩。

trans-unit.source: The access mask for this <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 這個 <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> 物件的存取遮罩。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> object associated with this <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定與這個 <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> 物件相關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> object associated with this <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 與這個 <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> 物件關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: No restrictions are placed on the <xref:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier> object.
